aa24c50e pf-r pf-r-eh" data-pf-type="Row" style="--pf-s-lg:15px; --pf-s-md:15px; --pf-s-sm:15px; --pf-s-xs:15px;"><div class="sc-drKuOJ bejofX pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--6 pf-c-md--6 pf-c-lg--6"><div class="sc-gRnDUn fJTCAC pf-af8ae0b2" data-pf-type="Column"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-hcmgZB ijGtLm pf-2d8c92b6"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jMMfwr doiSif pf-d61d91ac"><span style="font-weight: bold;">What are the symptoms of anxiety?<br><br></span>Commons signs of anxiety include:&nbsp;<br><br>• Feeling nervous, restless or tense<br>• Overthinking<br>• Increased heart rate or palpitations<br>• Trouble breathing<br>• Sweating<br>• Panic attacks<br>• Headaches<br>• Feeling weak or tired<br>• Constant worrying<br>• Having trouble sleeping<br>• Stomach issues<br>• Avoidance.</span></p></div></div><div class="sc-drKuOJ bejofX pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--6 pf-c-md--6 pf-c-lg--6"><div class="sc-gRnDUn fJTCAC pf-8762e6dc" data-pf-type="Column"><img sizes="(min-width: 992px) 1200px, (min-width: 768px) and (max-width: 991px) 800px, 400px" srcset="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/t/33/assets/pf-ab20dd84--Coping-with-Covid19-2-Online-Training-Course-The-Mandatory-Training-Group-UK-.jpg?v=1585550279 1200w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/t/33/assets/pf-ab20dd84--Coping-with-Covid19-2-Online-Training-Course-The-Mandatory-Training-Group-UK-_800x533.jpg?v=1585550279&resized 800w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/t/33/assets/pf-ab20dd84--Coping-with-Covid19-2-Online-Training-Course-The-Mandatory-Training-Group-UK-_400x267.jpg?v=1585550279&resized 400w" class="sc-kcDeIU gBYbwM pf-78a18983" data-pf-type="Image2"></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="sc-sdtwF iIwwEJ pf-448aa069 pf-r pf-r-eh" data-pf-type="Row" style="--pf-s-lg:15px; --pf-s-md:15px; --pf-s-sm:15px; --pf-s-xs:15px;"><div class="sc-drKuOJ bejofX pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--6 pf-c-md--6 pf-c-lg--6"><div class="sc-gRnDUn fJTCAC pf-2e8a5bf0" data-pf-type="Column"><img s